11
00:00:26,876 --> 00:00:28,500
Yang?

12
00:00:30,334 --> 00:00:32,417
Ela não falou com você?

13
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:35,250
Stanford e Columbia
estão brigando por ela,

14
00:00:35,334 --> 00:00:37,250
